| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0674 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f5973cbe-2046-5f1b-ac6e-ef8a1186e9a8"
